\SM[double]\SE[15]Right?! With this, we can make the perfect
Flower Crown...!

\SE[49]Um, um...? I, uh, \SE[37]have something I want to ask
Lunaroa...
\SE[49]When we grow up... [1]What will we become...?
\SM[nod]\SE[18]Sure! I want to marry Laura too!

\SE[4]But my dad said that you can only get married if it's
between a man and a woman...

\SE[9]I heard from the Traveling Poet-san! \\SE[15]They said that
in a country called Yurishin, girls can get married to each
other!

which one do you prefer?

\SE[18]Laura can choose! \SE[3]...Ah! How about the taller one
becomes the bride and the smaller one becomes the wife?

year... \!\SE[57]I won't be able to come back for another 5
years...

\SE[15]It's okay! I'll wait forever! \!\SE[16]I'll wait until
Luna becomes amazing and comes back!

\SE[56]Really...? \!\SE[57]If that much time passes... Will you
forget about me...? \!\SE[42]Won't you stop liking me...?

\SE[9]There's no way that would happen! \!\SE[24]I'll always love
you! \.I'll wait forever!

\SE[14]Awawa... Don't cry, Laura... \SE[25]But thank you... I was
a little worried. \SE[0]I'm going now... \SE[15]Will you wait for
me?

\SM[nod]\SE[16]... Yeah! \!\SE[15] Then let's get married when
you come back!

\SE[9]... I've got it! \SE[15] Luna, since you love reading
books, I'll make a bookmark that you can use over there too!
